item.title: Coding Platform
item.description: Introduction: I would like to explain one of the interesting projects that i have worked on , It is the creating a coding platform like leetcode. Being from a Computer Science Background , leetcode is the one thing i been doing for so long , One day i really wanted to learn about the system / design of leetcode and how these coding platform work , how online judges work .
